            <li>
                <p class="question">1. What is Injaz Connector For Edara ERP?</p>
                <p class="answer">Injaz Connector For Edara ERP is an integration tool that syncs sales orders, customer data, and inventory between the Salla e-commerce platform and the Edara ERP system. It helps businesses automate processes, streamline operations, and improve data accuracy.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">2. How does the integration work?</p>
                <p class="answer">The integration works by automatically syncing sales orders, customer profiles, and shipping addresses from Salla to the Edara ERP system. It also synchronizes inventory levels and pricing from Edara back to Salla to keep the information updated across platforms in real time.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">3. Is the data synchronization in real-time?</p>
                <p class="answer">Yes, Injaz Connector For Edara ERP ensures real-time data synchronization between Salla and Edara ERP, allowing businesses to have up-to-date information on orders, inventory, and customer data.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">4. What kind of information is synced?</p>
                <p class="answer">We sync sales orders, customer details (such as names, addresses, and contact information), inventory levels, and product pricing. This ensures accurate data across both systems.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">5. How do I set up the integration?</p>
                <p class="answer">Setting up the integration is simple. After signing up, follow the step-by-step guide provided in the app to connect your Salla store and Edara ERP system. You’ll need your account credentials for both platforms.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">6. Is my data secure?</p>
                <p class="answer">Absolutely. We use industry-standard encryption and secure servers to protect your data during synchronization and storage. Additionally, we follow strict privacy policies to ensure your information is handled responsibly.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p class="question">7. Can I customize the fields being synced?</p>
                <p class="answer">Yes, Injaz Connector For Edara ERP allows you to customize which fields are synced between Salla and Edara ERP. This gives you control over the data flow to meet your business needs.</p>
            </li>
